                ]
              },
              {
                "item_values": [],
                "key": "Tutorial",
                "string_values": [
                  "<p>This ancient Legatus Golem uses its sturdy marble body to defend against attack while using music and searing flames to obliterate its foes. Use <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 225, 75)\">methods suited to dealing with Geo</span> to break through its defenses. Apart from this, it will also set up resonators in combat that will assist its attacks. <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 225, 75)\">Destroy these resonators</span> to deplete its shielding effectively.</p>"
                ]
              }
